Nginx from source
**Depndencies**

sudo apt-get install libpcre3 libpcre3-dev  libpcrecpp0 libssl-dev zlib1g-dev make

wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.9.9.tar.gz

 ./configure -sbin-path=/usr/sbin/nginx --error-log-path=/var/log/nginx/error.log --http-log-path=/var/log/nginx/access.log --with-debug --with-pcre --with-http_ssl_module

 make

 sudo make install

 Add nginx to services

 download init script https://www.nginx.com/resources/wiki/start/topics/examples/initscripts/

 https://github.com/JasonGiedymin/nginx-init-ubuntu
 


 Add nginx conf file location:

NGINX_CONF_FILE=/etc/nginx/nginx.conf
DAEMON=/usr/bin/nginx
